26:32.717 --> 26:35.333
of strong, steady,

26:35.887 --> 26:38.378
experienced administration.

26:38.473 --> 26:40.509
(APPLAUSE)

26:41.726 --> 26:43.762
(APPLAUSE)

26:46.689 --> 26:51.149
(ALL SINGING)
Land of hope and glory

26:51.402 --> 26:55.691
Mother of the free

26:55.823 --> 26:58.815
How shall we extol thee...

26:58.910 --> 27:00.992
Congratulations, sir.

