Dr. Moran is here for you.

27:05.875 --> 27:06.864
(SLURPING)

27:10.213 --> 27:14.047
DR. MORAN:
Yes, you just won a general election,

27:16.719 --> 27:18.880
but 155 over 90.

27:19.514 --> 27:21.379
